{"tid":2074448,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"投資基金公會調查：逾7成受訪者未來1年擬投資港股","createTime":"2020-06-22T06:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T07:16:43.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"936aacdd1129b7ed2228aef863d9b5ec3b06774b","tid":2074448,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"投資基金公會調查：逾7成受訪者未來1年擬投資港股<br />\n2020-06-22 HKT 13:17<br />\n<br />\n香港投資基金公會的調查指出，雖然面對疫情衝擊及經濟下行，大部分散戶投資者仍然留意入市機會，逾7成受訪者表示，未來1年會繼續考慮投資港股，36%計劃在未來3個月投資股票。<br />\n<br />\n調查在5月訪問了710個散戶投資者，全部人均月入3萬元以上的中產階級，發現早前疫情導致股市出現調整，較年輕投資者的風險胃納降低，42%受訪的80、90後散戶表示擔心投資風險，較年長的投資者則只有24%表示憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533399-20200622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533399-20200622.htm&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F1A4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=6f5c8d00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533399-20200622.htm&h=93542cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533399-20200622.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d8c3e69f56e874ef47cc0c64f738d56ead72db2d","tid":2074448,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走資會話晒比人聽咩"},{"pid":"27d08710ae84817222ceb3da8f2c0217e809d4ec","tid":2074448,"uid":181418,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"3萬已經叫中產？"},{"pid":"a8f3b1598f20b5744b525b4c27a2c1d4a9178d9c","tid":2074448,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"太平盛世嗰陣時撚有人做呢啲研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae56ae62d